<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>PathProbe — web — example.com</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
    body{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;margin:0;background:#f5f7fa;color:#1a1a2e}
    header{background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;padding:1.5rem 2rem}
    header h1{margin:0 0 .25rem;font-size:1.4rem;letter-spacing:.01em}
    header .meta{font-size:.85rem;opacity:.72}
    .container{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:1.5rem 2rem}
    #map{height:420px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:1.75rem;border:1px solid #d1d5db;background:#e9ecef}
    .notice{background:#fef3c7;border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;padding:.75rem 1rem;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:.875rem}
    .notice code{background:#fff3;padding:.1em .3em;border-radius:3px}
    .geo-cards{display:flex;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1.75rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .geo-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;padding:1rem 1.5rem;flex:1;min-width:240px}
    .geo-card h3{margin:0 0 .5rem;font-size:.78rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:#6b7280}
    .geo-card .ip{font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace;color:#111827}
    .geo-card .detail{font-size:.85rem;color:#4b5563;margin-top:.2rem}
    section{margin-bottom:2rem}
    section h2{font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 .75rem;color:#111827;font-weight:600}
    table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;background:#fff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e5e7eb}
    thead th{background:#f9fafb;padding:.6rem .875rem;text-align:left;font-size:.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;color:#6b7280;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb;white-space:nowrap}
    tbody td{padding:.6rem .875rem;font-size:.875rem;border-bottom:1px solid #f3f4f6;font-family:monospace}
    tbody td.txt{font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif}
    tbody tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
    .ok  td:first-child{border-left:3px solid #10b981}
    .fail td:first-child{border-left:3px solid #ef4444}
    .warn td:first-child{border-left:3px solid #f59e0b}
    .badge{display:inline-block;padding:.2rem .55rem;border-radius:999px;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;font-family:system-ui;letter-spacing:.04em}
    .badge-ok{background:#d1fae5;color:#065f46}
    .badge-fail{background:#fee2e2;color:#991b1b}
    footer{text-align:center;padding:2rem;font-size:.78rem;color:#9ca3af}
    footer a{color:#9ca3af}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>PathProbe Diagnostic Report</h1>
  <p class="meta">Target: <strong>web</strong> &mdash; <strong>example.com</strong> &mdash; 2026-03-08 20:22:25</p>
</header>
<div class="container">

  
  <div class="notice">
    Geo-IP database not configured &mdash; map unavailable.
    Use <code>--geo-db-city</code> and <code>--geo-db-asn</code> to enable location visualisation.
  </div>
  

  <div class="geo-cards">
    <div class="geo-card">
      <h3>Client &mdash; Public IP</h3>
      <div class="ip">—</div>
    </div>
    <div class="geo-card">
      <h3>Target Host</h3>
      <div class="ip">example.com</div>
      <div class="detail">IP: 2606:4700::6812:1b78</div>
      <div class="detail">Location unavailable</div>
      
    </div>
  </div>

  

  

</div>
<footer>Generated by PathProbe &mdash; Map: <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/">OpenStreetMap</a> &amp; <a href="https://leafletjs.com/">Leaflet</a> &mdash; Geo: GeoLite2 by MaxMind</footer>
</body>
</html>
